{
  "name": "Crisis AI: Emergency Management Platform",
  "description": "An AI-powered dashboard for real-time disaster monitoring, risk assessment, and response coordination. It leverages generative AI to analyze incoming reports, generate action plans, and provide multilingual alerts."
